EN:
I will come here when I want to drink beer at night;

The ingredients are fresh and delicious, the environment is clean and comfortable, and the price is slightly higher. The light atmosphere of the izakaya is suitable for diners who do not hurry up.

There are not many tables, there are children's special tableware, the service is cordial;

If you do n’t eat half -cooked eggs, and you are a bit oolong noodles, please remember to say to the service staff first, “the eggs must be cooked”;
